title: What is Notion?
content: Notion is an all-in-one productivity tool that allows you to create notes, databases, and collaborative workspaces, making it easy to organize and manage your tasks, projects, and ideas in one place.

title: Who is this template for?
content: This template is made for people who want to make a website quickly with a Notion-themed style and prefer to use a template.

title: Do I need to pay for this?
content: No, this is free. All content on this template are dummy data.

title: Where can I ask more questions about this template?
content: If you have any further questions or need assistance regarding this template, please feel free to reach out to me on my website, or click the Contact within the navigation links.
